GOROVICH is a Psytrance producer and DJ known for his innovative style and sound. He has performed on some of the biggest dance floors around the world, bringing a hypnotic vibration to his audiences.
Nimrod Gorovich's journey as a musician began as a drummer in the Tel Aviv indie scene. He later transitioned into the electronic world and founded the groundbreaking duo "Empirikal," became a part of the legendary project "Loud," and ultimately created his solo project as GOROVICH. 
In his constant exploration and experimentation with new sounds and approaches to music, he continues to push the boundaries of Psytrance with his unique and captivating style.

With past releases on TIP Records and Hommega, GOROVICH joined Iboga Records with his debut album ‘Vortex’. His musical arsenal contains remixes and collaborations, including Ace Ventura, Captain Hook, LOUD, Eat Static, Juno Reactor, Out Of Orbit, Psysex, Eitan Reiter, Skizologic, Dekel, Perfect Stranger, Dori Sadovnik (aka Red Axes) and many more.
GOROVICH has played in countless festivals and venues, including: Ozora Festival, Boom Festival, Psy-Fi Festival, Babilon, Adhana, Mandallha, Baoba, Nibiri, and the list goes on – Promising a unique vibrating musical experience.

GOROVICH is a Producer/DJ that has redefined Psytrance. His signature sound combines funky rhythms with pure analog synths, to create a hypnotic result that has proven itself again and again on the biggest dance floors around the globe.

From his days as a fierce drummer in the Tel Aviv indie scene, through founding the duo Empirikal, live drumming with the legendary LOUD, and ultimately exploding onto the Psytrance scene with his solo project, Nimrod Gorovich is on a never-ending search for the next unique sound—and the embracing audience is right there along with him for the ride.

With past releases on TIP Records and Hommega, GOROVICH is signed to Iboga Records and FM Booking.
Some collaborations and remixes include: Ace Ventura, Captain Hook, LOUD, Eat Static, Juno Reactor, Out Of Orbit,
Psysex, Eitan Reiter, Skizologic, Dekel, Perfect Stranger, Dori Sadovnik (aka Red Axes).

GOROVICH has played in countless festivals and venues, including: Ozora Festival, Boom Festival, Psy-Fi Festival, Babilon, Adhana, Mandallha, Baoba, Nibiri, and many more.
